      <title>桑坦德银行亚洲区首席银行家嘉理盖思将离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/santander-s-top-banker-in-asia-gonzalo-garrigues-said-to-depart-lender</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，桑坦德银行亚太区企业融资主管贡萨洛·加里格斯 (Gonzalo Garrigues) 已辞去这家西班牙银行驻香港的职务。]]></description>
